high_descs: Turn to the right to face white table.
Pick up yellow-handled knife from the table.
Turn left, turn right to face table.
Put knife in square black bowl on the table.
Pick up bowl with knife in it.
Turn all the way around and come back to face white table with small black table to its left.
Put the bowl on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a knife in it on the black table.

high_descs: Turn to the right to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Step to the left and face the bowl.
Place the knife in the bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the knife in it.
Take a step to the left and face the black table.
Place the bowl with knife in it on the black table.
anns.task_desc: To put a knife in a bowl as well as move the bowl to the black table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn and go to the table.
Put the knife in the container on the table.
Pick up the container on the table.
Turn and go to the shelves next to the table.
Put the container on top of the shelves.
anns.task_desc: Move the container from the table to the shelves.

high_descs: Move to the table to the right of you.
Pick up a knife on the table.
Move to the left a few steps to the left side of the table.
Place the knife in a bowl on the table.
Pick up the bowl from the table.
Move a few steps to the left to a black end table.
Place the bowl on the end table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a knife on the black end table.

high_descs: Turn to the right, face the white table
Pick up the yellow knife from the table
Put the yellow knife in the blue bowl
Pick up the blue bowl from the table
Walk to the left
Stand in front of the black table
Put the blue bowl with the knife on the black table
anns.task_desc: Put the yellow knife and blue bowl on to the black table
